I would like to thank those who have contributed to this work.

This work is an arduous and brave combination for me since medicine is not my specialized field, so I have to investigate more. The biomedical engineering field is still a great challenge for me, but I hope it would be good proof and inspire my research in other cross-cutting and multi-field research.
